name: Daniel's Toolset
body:
# Welcome to Daniel's Toolset!
Here you can find many tools written in JavaScript, C# and some other languages. All of them are provided as free open-source tools, which you can simply use online or download them to your computer.

## Notice
This site is currently in development. Changes might be made without prior notice. Check out some time later---and you may find a brand new site!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
